Package: pollsDK
Type: Package
Title: Danish political polls
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mikkel Freltoft Krogsholm
Maintainer: Mikkel Freltoft Krogsholm <mikkel@56n.dk>
Description: Pulls current and historic Danish polling data from various 
   resources. Those sources are:
   Erik Gahners Github Repository: <https://github.com/erikgahner/polls>.
   Berlingske Barometer: <https://www.b.dk/politiko/barometeret>.
   Ritzau Index: <https://www.ritzau.dk/index>.
   DR VÃ¦lgervandring: <https://www.dr.dk/nyheder/politik/vaelgervandringer>.
